<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Activation</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset default styles */
    body,
    h1,
    p,
    a {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    /* Main container */
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    /* Logo */
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
    }

    /* Content */
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    /* Title */
    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Description */
    .description {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Button */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      color: #888888;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://escraowme.cyclic.app/rahmoun-logo1.png" alt="Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="title">Account Activation</h1>
      <p class="description">hi {{name}} Welcome to our platform! Please activate your account by clicking the button below.</p>
      <p class="description">If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <a class="button" href="{{token}}">Activate Account</a>
      <p class="description">If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>For any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@example.com">contact@Escrawme.com</a>.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2023 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>